  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to Senate",
    "asOf": "2022-09-15",
    "date": "2023-08-30T16:23:04Z",
    "text": "Taiwan Policy Act of 2022\n\nThis bill provides support to Taiwan and addresses related issues.\n\nFor example, the bill (1) establishes a comprehensive training program with Taiwan's government to familiarize the U.S. military and Taiwan's military with each other and achieve interoperability, and (2) authorizes the Department of State to take actions to help Taiwan become a non-borrowing member of the Inter-American Development Bank."
  },
